      "span_text": "From these Fig. 1 . The X-ray structure of GS ((cyclo-Pro-Val-Orn-Leu-dPhe)2) [CITATION_1] showing its four intra-molecular hydrogen bonding interactions (top view without side-chains for clarity reasons) and its amphiphilic characteristics, in which the hydrophobic side-chains of the Val and Leu residues are on one side of the molecule and the positively charged side-chains of the two Orn residues on the opposing side (side view)."
